Moin Khan has broken the record for most dismissals (104) in ODIs for PAK, going past Rashid Latif's 103
de Silva and Atapattu's 184-run partnership is SL's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 183 between Gurusinha and de Silva
